data.description: Home qualifies for a 2% 3/2/1 interest rate buy down. $9,000 will be paid towards a %2 interest rate buy down. 8 minutes to the beach, 20 minutes to Jupiter, 20 minutes to Boca. This is the definition of centrally located. BEAT THE INSURANCE COMPANIES, $3K is what you will pay here in this latest generation of construction. Very private home, totally fenced in, security cameras, $150/month pays your Water, Sewer, Trash, and Electric with it's 35KW solar array (1 of 65 properties grandfathered in Lake Worth Beach with over size), screened in porch, firepit patio, lush landscaping, updated kitchen with granite and stainless steel appliances.
